                <span class="field-content"><a href="/periods/tudors/elizabethan-social-and-economic-legislation"><h3 class="title">Elizabethan Social and Economic Legislation</h3></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-phpcode">
                <span class="field-content">Social and economic legislation occupied a great deal of time in Elizabethan Parliaments and was considered, after the granting of taxation, to be the primary function of the House of Commons. Hundreds of bills were initiated concerning industries such as the manufacture and trade of cloth,...</span>
  </div>
  
